The SeaTac Council makes policy, land use, and budget decisions to be carried out by the City Manager.

The following documents provide more information:

City of SeaTac State Legislative Agenda 2025
City Council Administrative Procedures
Council Expenditure Report
Council Representation - Council Matrix

Quarterly attendance reports can be found in document central: https://www.seatacwa.gov/government/document-central/-folder-4610.
